            <thetext>As &quot;native page scrolling&quot; is not possible anymore because of tablet support, the only chance is to use &quot;webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch&quot;.

on iOS:
The performance of the animations do not improve by using &quot;webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch&quot;.

On Android devices, the performance with webkit-overflow-scrolling is even worse. 

So we should make the usage of &quot;webkit-overflow-scrolling&quot; optional, and recommend it only for iOS devices.</thetext>
